description:
Vendormate, the leader in healthcare vendor credentialing, is putting vendor
credentialing into the palm of your hands with mobile features that keep you on the
go.

FREE to Every Healthcare Representative with a Vendormate profile
+ Hospital Sign Out – Skip the kiosk and sign out on your phone. Sign out
your colleagues too.
+ Snap and send photos of documents to your Vendormate profile straight
from your phone.

FREE to Vendormate Corporate Accounts
+ Hotline to live Vendormate Support agents with one touch
+ Tap into a nationwide database of hospitals to find contacts and locations

More capabilities are coming soon. 

Vendormate Mobile - making healthcare vendor
credentialing as mobile as you are
releaseNotes:
Vendormate, the leader in healthcare vendor credentialing, is putting vendor credentialing in the palm of your hands with mobile features that keep you on the go.  

FREE to Every Healthcare Representative with a Vendormate profile
+  Document Upload - Snap and send photos of documents from your phone to be uploaded to your Vendormate profile
+  Bypass the Sign-in Kiosk - Print your badge from home and sign in on your phone (Available at participating hospital locations)
+  Hospital Sign Out - Skip the kiosk and sign out on your phone.  Sign out your colleagues, too.

FREE to Vendormate Corporate Accounts
+ Hotline to live Vendormate support agents with one touch
+ Tap into a nationwide database of hospitals to find locations and the vendor credentialing organization

More features coming soon.

Vendormate Mobile - making healthcare vendor credentialing as mobile as you are.
